      About this item

      • Remote Control: The ZBM5 is a Zigbee-based smart wall switch. With this smart switch, you can control your home lights from anywhere with just a tap on your phoneno need to walk around the house. (Note: Requires SONOFF Zigbee Gateway.)
      • Neutral Wire Optional: No need to worry about whether this switch will fit your home's wiring setup. The smart light switch can be used with or without a neutral wire
      • Open-Source Platform Compatibility: In addition to eWeLink app control, you can connect the Zigbee switch to Home Assistant via Zigbee2MQTT, enabling seamless integration with devices from various manufacturers
      • Voice Control On/Off: When your hands are busy, simply use voice commands to control the interruptor inteligente. Bind your voice assistant account to the eWeLink app, then you can easily manage your lights through Alexa or Google Home smart speakers
      • Timers and Scene Automation: With the eWeLink app, you can set scheduled on/off times for your lights or create smart scenes. For example, the lights at your entryway will automatically turn on when you open the door

      • Does this wall switch need a neutral wire to install?

        This device can be used in a switch box with or without a neutral wire.

        Note: Only when the neutral wire is connected, the device acts as a zigbee network router.

      • In addition to physical button controlwhat can I use to control this smart switch?

        1. eWeLink app: Required a SONOFF hub. First add the hub to the app (2.4GHZ network is required), and add ZBM5 from the hub

        2. Home assistant

        3. Add your voice assistant account (such as Alexa, Google home) in eWeLink app to voice control your switch

      • Which SONOFF gateways can support the features of this device?

        The following SONOFF gateways are supported: ZBBridge-P (V2.2.0), ZBBridge-U (V1.5.0), NSPanel Pro (V3.7.0), iHost (V2.5.0), ZBDongle-P, ZBDongle-E.

      • What features can I get from third party devices?

        Add your voice assistant account from eWeLink app to get voice control to turn on and off.

        Note that the device is not compatible with these third party gateways, to get the full feature experience, please use the SONOFF gateway mentioned above!

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
